# Storage + IPC Rules

Rules:
- Mutable runtime data must live under `%LOCALAPPDATA%/SpecterStudio/` or user-configured settings paths.
- Do not write mutable data into `resources/` or `app.asar`.
- Keep JSON profile storage backward compatible.
- IPC must validate inputs and avoid leaking internal file paths or secrets.
- Preload APIs must stay stable unless all renderer call sites are updated.
- For packaging/offline changes, run `npm run validate:offline` when possible.
